Interface ReferenceAs<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - the type of the reference after mapping
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface ReferenceAs<M>
extends ValueMapper, ReferenceMapper
    A ReferenceMapper that provides a default behavior to use M instead of Id for references.
